---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Authority Roadmap" description="Credibility roadmap and milestones for Whitfield Research Partners.">
  <div class="container" style="padding-top:4rem;padding-bottom:4rem;max-width:820px;">
    <h1>Authority Roadmap</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--color-muted);margin-top:0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">
      Building research authority is a multi-year effort. This roadmap tracks our progress from foundation to scale.
    </p>

    <div style="display:grid;gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2rem;">
      <div style="background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.5rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin:0;font-size:1.25rem;">Phase 1 — Foundation</h2>
          <span style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;padding:0.2rem 0.6rem;border-radius:999px;background:#DCFCE7;color:#166534;">Done</span>
        </div>
        <ul style="margin-top:1rem;padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;color:var(--color-muted);">
          <li>Published methodology, editorial policy, and disclosure policy.</li>
          <li>Named independent reviewer program established.</li>
          <li>Initial category definitions and coverage table published.</li>
          <li>First two original reports published with full frontmatter.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.5rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin:0;font-size:1.25rem;">Phase 2 — Depth</h2>
          <span style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;padding:0.2rem 0.6rem;border-radius:999px;background:#FEF3C7;color:#92400E;">In Progress</span>
        </div>
        <ul style="margin-top:1rem;padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;color:var(--color-muted);">
          <li>Expand source diversity for each active category.</li>
          <li>Move all live reports through independent review.</li>
          <li>Introduce annual review cycles for core benchmarks.</li>
          <li>Publish first correction log and evidence-response analysis.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.5rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin:0;font-size:1.25rem;">Phase 3 — Scale</h2>
          <span style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;padding:0.2rem 0.6rem;border-radius:999px;background:#E2E8F0;color:#475569;">Future</span>
        </div>
        <ul style="margin-top:1rem;padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;color:var(--color-muted);">
          <li>Add four to six new active categories.</li>
          <li>Launch archived report versioning for transparency.</li>
          <li>Develop machine-readable research outputs and API access.</li>
          <li>Publish annual methodology review and reviewer rotation report.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top:3rem;">Quarterly Targets</h2>
    <ul style="margin-top:1rem;padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
      <li><strong>Q3 2026:</strong> Publish two additional category benchmarks.</li>
      <li><strong>Q4 2026:</strong> Complete independent review of all live reports.</li>
      <li><strong>Q1 2027:</strong> Launch correction log and reader evidence portal.</li>
      <li><strong>Q2 2027:</strong> Expand to six active categories.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
